ğŸ“¦ What is Packet Sniffer CLI?

Packet Sniffer CLI is a command-line tool that captures real-time network packets and provides:

Source/Destination IP & ports

Protocol identification (TCP, UDP, ICMP, ARP, DNS)

Logging to human-readable files

Saving to PCAP for Wireshark

Filtering by protocol/IP/port

